Paper: hep-th/9811001

Date: 1998-10-31

Title: Abelian Bosonization, the Wess-Zumino Functional and Conformal Symmetry

Authors: A. Bogojevic, B. Sazdovic (Belgrade, Inst. Phys.) and O. Miskovic

(Vinca Inst.)Comments: 7 pages, Latex 2e, no figures

We look at the equivalence of the massive Thirring and sine-Gordon models.Previously, this equivalence was derived perturbatively in mass (though to allorders). Our calculation goes beyond that and uncovers an underlying conformalsymmetry.